 N00088: RD         R61.0   ;(OPRQST0 )  
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"

                    2
                    1
                    R60     ;(OPOSFT  ) "OP OUTPUT GROUP SHIFT"
 N00089: RD         R60.0   ;(OPO1GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 1GROUP"
         OR         R60.2   ;(OPO3GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 3GROUT"
         OR         R60.4   ;(OPO5GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 5GROUT"
         OR         R60.6   ;(OPO7GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 7GROUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         WRT        R29.0   ;(OPOGRP1 )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP1"
 N00090: RD         R60.1   ;(OPO2GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 2GROUP"
         OR         R60.2   ;(OPO3GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 3GROUT"
         OR         R60.5   ;(OPO6GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 6GROUT"
         OR         R60.6   ;(OPO7GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 7GROUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         WRT        R29.1   ;(OPOGRP2 )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP2"
 N00091: RD         R60.3   ;(OPO4GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 4GROUT"
         OR         R60.4   ;(OPO5GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 5GROUT"
         OR         R60.5   ;(OPO6GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 6GROUT"

 N00092: RD         R60.7   ;(OPO8GRP )   "OP OUTPUT 8GROUT"

         WRT        R29.3   ;(OPOGRP4 )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP4"
 N00093: RD         Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"
         AND.NOT    Y34.1   ;(Y341    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 2BIT"
         AND.NOT    Y34.2   ;(Y342    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 3BIT"
         AND.NOT    Y34.3   ;(Y343    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 4BIT"
         WRT        R63.0   ;(1GRPO   )   "1GROUP OUTPUT"
 N00094: RD.NOT     Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

         AND.NOT    Y34.2   ;(Y342    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 3BIT"
         AND.NOT    Y34.3   ;(Y343    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 4BIT"
         WRT        R63.1   ;(2GRPO   )   "2GROUP OUTPUT"
 N00095: RD         Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

         AND.NOT    Y34.2   ;(Y342    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 3BIT"
         AND.NOT    Y34.3   ;(Y343    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 4BIT"
         WRT        R63.2   ;(3GRPO   )   "3GROUP OUTPUT"
 N00096: RD.NOT     Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

 N00097: RD         Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

 N00098: RD.NOT     Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

 N00099: RD         Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

         AND        Y34.2   ;(Y342    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 3BIT"

 N00100: RD.NOT     Y34.0   ;(Y340    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 1BIT"

         AND        Y34.3   ;(Y343    )   "OP OUTPUT GROUP 4BIT"

 N00101: RD         R63.0   ;(1GRPO   )   "1GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"
         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R30     ;(R0030   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00102: RD         R63.1   ;(2GRPO   )   "2GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"
         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R32     ;(R0032   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00103: RD         R63.2   ;(3GRPO   )   "3GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"
         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"

         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R34     ;(R0034   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00104: RD         R63.3   ;(4GRPO   )   "4GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"

         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"

                    R36     ;(R0036   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00105: RD         R63.4   ;(5GRPO   )   "5GROUP OUTPUT"

         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"

         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R38     ;(R0038   )

 N00106: RD         R63.5   ;(6GRPO   )   "6GROUP OUTPUT"

         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R40     ;(R0040   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00107: RD         R63.6   ;(7GRPO   )   "7GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"
         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R42     ;(R0042   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00108: RD         R63.7   ;(8GRPO   )   "8GROUP OUTPUT"
         AND        R50.3   ;(OPPH4   )   "OP PHASE 4"
         AND.NOT    R50.4   ;(OPRQST  )   "OP REQUEST STATUS"
         AND.NOT    R50.5   ;(OPRQVER )   "OP REQUEST VERSION"
         AND.NOT    R62.0   ;(OPCLR1  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 1"
         AND.NOT    R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R44     ;(R0044   )
                    Y32     ;(OPODATA ) "OP OUTPUT DATA"
 N00109: RD         R58.0   ;(OPIGRP1 )   "INPUT GRP 1"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R10     ;(OPGP1D  )
 N00110: RD         R58.1   ;(OPIGRP2 )   "INPUT GRP 2"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R12     ;(OPGP2D  )
 N00111: RD         R58.2   ;(OPIGRP3 )   "INPUT GRP 3"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R14     ;(OPGP3D  )
 N00112: RD         R58.3   ;(OPIGRP4 )   "INPUT GRP 4"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R16     ;(OPGP4D  )
 N00113: RD         R58.4   ;(OPIGRP5 )   "INPUT GRP 5"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R18     ;(OPGP5D  )
 N00114: RD         R58.5   ;(OPIGRP6 )   "INPUT GRP 6"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R20     ;(OPGP6D  )
 N00115: RD         R58.6   ;(OPIGRP7 )   "INPUT GRP 7"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R22     ;(OPGP7D  )
 N00116: RD         R58.7   ;(OPIGRP8 )   "INPUT GRP 8"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R24     ;(OPGP8D  )
 N00117: RD         R59.1   ;(OPIGRPA )   "OP STATUS REQUEST GRP"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R46     ;(OPSTATUS) "DATA CHECK MONITRING"
 N00118: RD         R59.2   ;(OPIGRPB )   "VERSION REQUEST GRP"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         AND        R27.0   ;(1PC1    )   "1 PLUSE COUNTER1"
         AND        R200.0  ;(1PC2    )   "1 PULSE COUNTER 2"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
                    R48     ;(OPVER   ) "VERSION MONITRING"
 N00119: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         AND.NOT    R28.0   ;(SPARIERR)   "SLAVE PARITY ERROR CHECK"
         SUB        32      ; COMPB
                    1
                    60506
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
 N00120: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         AND        R9000.0 ;(X=Y     )   "COMPARE X=Y"
         WRT        R62.3   ;(OPCLRE1 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST1"
 N00121: RD         R62.3   ;(OPCLRE1 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST1"
         OR         R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         AND.NOT    R62.4   ;(OPCLRE2 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST2"
         AND.NOT    R62.5   ;(OPIGRPE3)   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST3"
         WRT        R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
 N00122: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         SUB        32      ; COMPB
                    1
                    60581
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
 N00123: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         AND        R9000.0 ;(X=Y     )   "COMPARE X=Y"
         AND        R62.1   ;(OPCLR2  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 2"
         WRT        R62.4   ;(OPCLRE2 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST2"
 N00124: RD         R62.4   ;(OPCLRE2 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST2"
         OR         R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         AND.NOT    R62.3   ;(OPCLRE1 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST1"
         AND.NOT    R62.5   ;(OPIGRPE3)   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST3"
         WRT        R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
 N00125: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         SUB        32      ; COMPB
                    1
                    60074
                    X32     ;(OPIDATA ) "OP INPUT DATA"
 N00126: RD         R59.5   ;(OPIGRPE )   "ALARM CLEAR REQUEST GRP"
         AND        R9000.0 ;(X=Y     )   "COMPARE X=Y"
         AND        R62.2   ;(OPCLR3  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR 3"
         WRT        R62.5   ;(OPIGRPE3)   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST3"
 N00127: RD         R62.5   ;(OPIGRPE3)   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST3"
         RD.STK     R62.6   ;(OPLCR4  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR4"
         AND.NOT    R50.0   ;(OPPH1   )   "OP PHASE 1"
         OR.STK     
         AND.NOT    R62.3   ;(OPCLRE1 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST1"
         AND.NOT    R62.4   ;(OPCLRE2 )   "OP ALARM CLEAR REQUEST2"
         WRT        R62.6   ;(OPLCR4  )   "OP ALARM CLEAR4"
 N00128: SUB        69      ; LBL  
                    L10 
(*
14 bit mode*)
 N00130: RD.NOT     R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         RD.STK     R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         AND.NOT    R2985.2 ;(IN=OUT  )   "CHANNEL NUMBER IS SAME(IN=OUT)"
         OR.STK     
         WRT        R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
 N00131: RD.NOT     R1101.0 ;(A       )   "LOGIC "1""
         RD.STK.NOT R1101.0 ;(A       )   "LOGIC "1""
         RD.STK     R2984.2 ;(CNTRST2 )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER RESET CMD"
         ORPT       A42.6   ;(2343    )   "THERMAL BOARD ERROR"
         RD.STK     R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         SUB        56      ; CTRB 
                    99
                    15
         WRT        R2984.0 ;(CNTFULL )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER FULL"
 N00132: RD         R2984.0 ;(CNTFULL )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER FULL"
         AND.NOT    R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         AND.NOT    R2984.2 ;(CNTRST2 )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER RESET CMD"
         WRT        R2984.1 ;(CNTRST1 )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER RESET AUX"
 N00133: RD         R2984.1 ;(CNTRST1 )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER RESET AUX"
         AND        R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         WRT        R2984.2 ;(CNTRST2 )   "THERMAL IO COUNTER RESET CMD"
 N00134: RD         C5196.0 ;(CNTODD  )  
         WRT        R2985.0 ;(ADC.Y   )   "REQUEST FOR AD CONVERTER INPUT"
 N00135: RD.NOT     R2985.0 ;(ADC.Y   )   "REQUEST FOR AD CONVERTER INPUT"
         SUB        282     ; SHRW 
                    C5196 
                    1
                    R2995   ;(REQ.CHA ) "REQUIRED CHANNEL NUMBER"
 N00136: RD         R2985.0 ;(ADC.Y   )   "REQUEST FOR AD CONVERTER INPUT"
         SUB        40      ; NUMEB
                    2
                    8
                    R2995   ;(REQ.CHA ) "REQUIRED CHANNEL NUMBER"
(*
14 bit, X INPUT READ*)
 N00138: RD         R1101.0 ;(A       )   "LOGIC "1""
         SUB        43      ; MOVB 
                    X13 
                    R2980   ;(TH.RAW  ) "RAW DATA FROM THERMAL IO BOARD"
 N00139: RD         R1101.0 ;(A       )   "LOGIC "1""
         SUB        8       ; MOVE 
                    0
                    11
                    X14 
                    R2981 
 N00140: RD         X14.2   ;(CHOO    )  
         WRT        R2986.0 ;(CH00A   )   "CHANNEL DATA1 FROM THERMAL IO"
 N00141: RD         X14.3   ;(CH01    )  
         WRT        R2986.1 ;(CH01A   )   "CHANNEL DATA2 FROM THERMAL IO"
 N00142: RD         X14.4   ;(CH02    )  
         WRT        R2986.2 ;(CH02A   )   "CHANNEL DATA3 FROM THERMAL IO"
 N00143: RD         X14.5   ;(CH03    )  
         WRT        R2986.3 ;(CH03A   )   "CHANNEL DATA4 FROM THERMAL IO"
 N00144: RD         R2986.3 ;(CH03A   )   "CHANNEL DATA4 FROM THERMAL IO"
         AND.NOT    R2986.2 ;(CH02A   )   "CHANNEL DATA3 FROM THERMAL IO"
         AND.NOT    R2986.1 ;(CH01A   )   "CHANNEL DATA2 FROM THERMAL IO"
         AND        R2986.0 ;(CH00A   )   "CHANNEL DATA1 FROM THERMAL IO"
         WRT        R2985.1 ;(ADC.X   )   "RECEIVED AD CONVERTER INPUT"
(*
14 bit, LVDT DATA OUTPUT*)
 N00146: RDPT       R2984.3 ;(LVDT.OK )   "LVDT DATA IS ARRIVED"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R2980   ;(TH.RAW  ) "RAW DATA FROM THERMAL IO BOARD"
                    R2982   ;(ADCOUT  ) "FINAL OUTPUT ADC CONVERT"
 N00147: RD         R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         SUB        323     ; SUBSW
                    R2986   ;(IN.CHAX ) "RECEIVED CHANNEL NUMBER"
                    1
                    R2993   ;(IN.CHA  ) "RECEIVED CHANNEL NUMBER"
 N00148: RD         R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         SUB        32      ; COMPB
                    1002
                    R2995   ;(REQ.CHA ) "REQUIRED CHANNEL NUMBER"
                    R2993   ;(IN.CHA  ) "RECEIVED CHANNEL NUMBER"
 N00149: RD         R2984.7 ;(SCANP   )   "THERMAL IO SCANNING PULSE"
         AND        R9000.0 ;(X=Y     )   "COMPARE X=Y"
         WRT        R2985.2 ;(IN=OUT  )   "CHANNEL NUMBER IS SAME(IN=OUT)"
(*
SENSOR DISCONNECTED ALARM BUILDING*)
 N00151: RDPT       R2985.3 ;(TEMP.OK )   "TEMPERATURE DATA IS ARRIVED"
         SUB        44      ; MOVW 
                    R2980   ;(TH.RAW  ) "RAW DATA FROM THERMAL IO BOARD"
                    R2989 
 N00152: RDPT       R2985.3 ;(TEMP.OK )   "TEMPERATURE DATA IS ARRIVED"
         SUB        201     ; EQW  
                    R2989 
                    512
         RDPT.STK   R2985.3 ;(TEMP.OK )   "TEMPERATURE DATA IS ARRIVED"
         SUB        201     ; EQW  
                    R2989 
                    522
         OR.STK     
         WRT        R2985.4 ;(SENS.OFF)   "SENSOR IS DISCONNECT"
 N00153: RDPT       R2985.3 ;(TEMP.OK )   "TEMPERATURE DATA IS ARRIVED"
         AND        R2985.4 ;(SENS.OFF)   "SENSOR IS DISCONNECT"
         SUB        293     ; BSETB
                    R2988 
                    R2993   ;(IN.CHA  ) "RECEIVED CHANNEL NUMBER"

                    R2990

 N02901: SUB        71      ; SP   
                    P400    ;(P400_MANUFACTURE) "MANUFACTURE LOGIC"

         SUB        40      ; NUMEB
                    2
                    50
                    R2870   ;(ASPRPM  ) "ACTUAL SPINDLE SPEED"
 N02903: RD         F1.7    ;(MA      )   "NC READY"
         SUB        40      ; NUMEB
                    2
                    0
                    R2876   ;(ASPRPM2 )
 N02904: RD         F1.7    ;(MA      )   "NC READY"
         SUB        40      ; NUMEB
                    2
                    0
                    R2878   ;(ASPRPM3 )
 N02905: RD         F1.7    ;(MA      )   "NC READY"
         SUB        51      ; WINDR
                    R2870   ;(ASPRPM  ) "ACTUAL SPINDLE SPEED"
         WRT        R2869.7 ;(ASSR    )   "ACTUAL SPINDLE SPEED READ"
 N02906: SUB        72      ; SPE  
 N02907: SUB        71      ; SP   
                    P901    ;(MCU_NC_RECV) "MACHINE MOVEMENT DETECT"
 N02908: RD         X105.6  ;(MMDX1.EI)   "MMD CLK RECEIVE"
         AND        X105.7  ;(MMDX2.EI)   "MMD DATA RECEIVE"
         WRT        D9279.5 ;(DATA_MCUNC)  
 N02909: RD         X105.6  ;(MMDX1.EI)   "MMD CLK RECEIVE"
         WRT        D9279.4 ;(CLK_MCUNC)  
 N02910: RD         D9279.0 ;(CNO_CTR_MCUNC)  
         RD.STK     D9279.1 ;(UD_CTR_MCUNC)  
         RD.STK     D9279.2 ;(RST_CTR_MCUNC)  
         RDPT.STK   D9279.4 ;(CLK_MCUNC)  
         SUB        55      ; CTRC 
                    D9280   ;(MCUNC_P ) "MCUNC_PRESET_PE_0"
                    D9282   ;(MCUNC_C ) "MCUNC_CURRENT_PE_0"
         WRT        D9279.3 ;(COIL_CTR_MCUNC)  
 N02911: RDPT       D9279.4 ;(CLK_MCUNC)  
         SUB        282     ; SHRW 
                    D9286   ;(MCUNC_DATA)
                    1
                    D9286   ;(MCUNC_DATA)
         WRT        D9279.6 ;(COIL_SHRW_MCUNC)  
 N02912: RDNT       D9279.5 ;(DATA_MCUNC)  
         SUB        272     ; ORW  
                    D9286   ;(MCUNC_DATA)
                    -32768
                    D9286   ;(MCUNC_DATA)
 N02913: RD         R9091.1 ;(L_EXEC  )   "LADDER EXECUTION STATUS SIGNAL"
         SUB        201     ; EQW  
                    D9282   ;(MCUNC_C ) "MCUNC_CURRENT_PE_0"
                    16
         WRT        D9288.1 ;(RECV_MCUNC)  
 N02914: RD         R9091.1 ;(L_EXEC  )   "LADDER EXECUTION STATUS SIGNAL"
         SUB        47      ; MOVD 
                    D9290   ;(MCUNC_E )
                    D9294   ;(MCUNC_F )
 N02915: RD.NOT     D9288.0 ;(SEND_NCMCU)  
         SUB        10      ; JMP  
                    0
 N02916: RD         D9288.0 ;(SEND_NCMCU)  
         AND        R9015.0 ;(L_EXES  )   "LADDER EXECUTION START SIGNAL"
         SUB        60      ; AND  
                    1
                    D9288 
                    11111110
                    D9288 
 N02917: RD.NOT     D9270.0 ;(SHCOIL_CTR_NCMCU)   "SELF-HOLD COIL for CLK COUNTER"
         AND.NOT    D9270.6 ;(CLK_GEN_NCMCU)   "CLK GEN from TIMER"
         SUB        24      ; TMRB 
                    273
                    50
         WRT        D9270.6 ;(CLK_GEN_NCMCU)   "CLK GEN from TIMER"
 N02918: RD         D9270.6 ;(CLK_GEN_NCMCU)   "CLK GEN from TIMER"
         AND.NOT    D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
         RD.STK.NOT D9270.6 ;(CLK_GEN_NCMCU)   "CLK GEN from TIMER"
         AND        D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
         OR.STK     
         WRT        D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
 N02919: RD         D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
         WRT        Y103.6  ;(MMDY1.EO)   "MMD CLK SEND"
 N02920: RD         D9270.2 ;(CNO_CTR_NCMCU)   "CNO for CLK COUNTER"
         RD.STK     D9270.3 ;(UD_CTR_NCMCU)   "UD for CLK COUNTER"
         RD.STK     D9270.4 ;(RST_CTR_NCMCU)   "RST for CLK COUNTER"
         RDPT.STK   D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
         SUB        55      ; CTRC 
                    D9271   ;(NCMCU_P ) "NCMCU_PRESET_PE_0"
                    D9273   ;(NCMCU_C ) "NCMCU_CURRENT_PE_0"
         WRT        D9270.5 ;(COIL_CTR_NCMCU)   "COIL for CLK COUNTER"
 N02921: RD         D9270.5 ;(COIL_CTR_NCMCU)   "COIL for CLK COUNTER"
         OR         D9270.0 ;(SHCOIL_CTR_NCMCU)   "SELF-HOLD COIL for CLK COUNTER"
         WRT        D9270.0 ;(SHCOIL_CTR_NCMCU)   "SELF-HOLD COIL for CLK COUNTER"
 N02922: RDPT       D9270.7 ;(CLK_NCMCU)   "CLK OUTPUT"
         SUB        282     ; SHRW 
                    D9277   ;(NCMCU_DATA)
                    1
                    D9277   ;(NCMCU_DATA)
         WRT        D9270.1 ;(COIL_SHRW_NCMCU)   "COIL for DATA SHRW"
 N02923: RD         D9270.1 ;(COIL_SHRW_NCMCU)   "COIL for DATA SHRW"
         OR         Y103.7  ;(MMDY2.EO)   "MMD DATA SEND"
         AND        Y103.6  ;(MMDY1.EO)   "MMD CLK SEND"
         WRT        Y103.7  ;(MMDY2.EO)   "MMD DATA SEND"
 N02924: RD         R9091.1 ;(L_EXEC  )   "LADDER EXECUTION STATUS SIGNAL"
         SUB        201     ; EQW  
                    D9273   ;(NCMCU_C ) "NCMCU_CURRENT_PE_0"
                    16
         WRT.NOT    D9288.0 ;(SEND_NCMCU)  
 N02925: SUB        30      ; JMPE 
 N02926: SUB        72      ; SPE  
 N02927: SUB        64      ; END
